[P1 Zangief Modifier (Select+L2: Normal; Select+R2: Mech)]
author=Hacc
description=This will allow you to change his moves at will without using a special. Other characters will be affected by this code. Replace the value "80" with 1 to make all characters stable. This will give you a semi-mech Zangief (minus the heaviness).
