[1st Fighter Codes\P1-1 - Character Modifier]
author=HackFreak
description=Only use the P1/P2 1st Fighter codes when playing as Abyss. When playing as Abyss, the game will rarely lock-up. Do not switch or perform double team special attacks when your playing as Abyss. Using the following attack command for Abyss, will lock-up the game. Also, don't turn on the command list, or the game will lock-up. Normally when you defeat Abyss, he would transform into his next transformation. You will not transform with this code. Another quick note: The game doesn't run well on certain versions of the PS2 and will lock-up occassionally. Don't ask me why, but it just does for some odd reason.

QCF+LK 
QCF= Quarter Circle Forward (D, DF, F) 
LK= Light Kick 

83 - Ryu 
84 - Zangief 
85 - Guile 
86 - Morrigan 
87 - Anakaris 
88 - Strider Hiryu 
